Package: JointMR
Type: Package
Title: JointMR: A joint likelihood-based approach for causal effect estimation using multiple GWAS summary databases in Mendelian randomization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Lei Hou", "Sijia Wu",
      email = "hou.lei.sph@sdu.edu.cn",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A framework to estimate causal effects by integrating repeated Mendelian Randomization (MR) information obtained from all exposure-outcome GWAS database pairings. JointMR evaluates correlation structures among GWAS databases, constructs pleiotropy-adjusted Wald ratios, estimates instrumental variable heterogeneity, and implements a relaxed-NOME extension to account for measurement errors.
